<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Thank You for Contacting | TMD GYM</title>
<meta name="description" content="Thank you for reaching out to TMD GYM! We will get back to you as soon as possible. In the meantime, explore our Muay Thai and fitness services.">
<meta name="keywords" content="Thank You, Contact Confirmation, TMD GYM, Contact Us, Gym Inquiry">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="56x56"
    href="../images/fav-icon/Black White Minimalist Professional Initial Logo.png">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #FF5E14;  /* Gym accent orange */
            --dark: #1E1E1E;     /* Dark background */
            --light: #F8F9FA;    /* Light text */
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--dark);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .thank-you-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.8), rgba(0,0,0,0.8)), url('../images/home/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b.avif');
            height: 100vh;
            background-size: cover;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .checkmark {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: bounce 1s;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .thank-you-message {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 94, 20, 0.3);
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {transform: translateY(0);}
            40% {transform: translateY(-30px);}
            60% {transform: translateY(-15px);}
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .thank-you-message {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="thank-you-hero">
        <div class="checkmark">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
        </div>
        <h1>MESSAGE <span style="color: var(--primary);">RECEIVED!</span></h1>
        
        <div class="thank-you-message">
            <p>Thank you for reaching out to <strong>ELITE FITNESS</strong>! We've received your message and our team will contact you within <strong>24 hours</strong>.</p>
            <p>While you wait, check out our training programs below:</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
            <a href="/workSchedule" class="cta-button">VIEW CLASSES</a>
            <a href="/" class="cta-button" style="background: #3498db;">HOME PAGE</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>Need immediate help? Call us: <strong>+ (212) - 613 211 334</strong></p>
            <p>Or visit our gym at: <strong>Near, Al Fath., Pharmacy DC, Morocco.</strong></p>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
